# Year and Semester Support Implementation Plan

Implement a robust Year and Semester management system for the Classroom Tracker, enabling historical data retention, automated term detection, and seamless roster importing from board CSVs.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Schema Migration**: This requires a database version bump (v19). Existing classes will be assigned to a default "Current" year/semester (e.g., 2025-26, Sem 2) during migration.
> [!WARNING]
> **Roster Import Conflicts**: The system will use the board's `studentId` as the unique anchor. If a student appears in multiple classes across years, their history will be aggregated under this ID.

